These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, crime, martial-arts, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, indie, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, brazilian, german, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, ship, subway, snowmobile
1. the brazilian is the fan of dubstep##1
2. the german is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching sports movies##2
3. the brazilian is the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the left of the malaysian##1
6. the person driving the subway is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the fan of disco is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
8. the malaysian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | sports   | disaster  | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | dubstep    | ambient      | indie    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | brazilian | german | malaysian |
| Transport     | snowmobile  | train       | ship    | subway     |

