.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, gardening, chess, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, time-travel, comedy, satire
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, horse, guinea-pig
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, sailing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person watching satire movies is between the owner of the horse and the person who's sport is badminton##2
6. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person watching satire movies and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading | gardening    | chess  | puzzles    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller      | time-travel  | satire  | comedy |
| Pet           | guinea-pig      | horse       | snake      | goldfish       |
| Sport         | cricket    | parkour | sailing | badminton |

