.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, pepper, corn, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, collecting, filmmaking, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, scientist, architect, firefighter
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, airplane, trike
1. the architect is the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the firefighter##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the scientist is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person eating kale is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person eating corn and the scientist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | pepper | corn     | kale   | cherry     |
| Hobby       | collecting   | hiking   | filmmaking | drawing |
| Job         | nurse   | architect | firefighter       | scientist    |
| Transport   | airplane    | jet-ski | scooter  | trike    |

