.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, analyst, musician, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, spy, time-travel, zombie
4 different pets are kept: horse, cat, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, cricket, surfing, parkour
 1. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching zombie movies is the accountant##1
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the cat##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is the musician##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the accountant is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the analyst is between the owner of the horse and the chef##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | accountant  | chef | analyst     | musician |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | sports  | time-travel | spy       |
| Pet           | cat       | mouse    | hedgehog      | horse           |
| Sport         | golf | cricket   | parkour   | surfing         |

