.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, avocado, grapes, pumpkin
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, pilot, fisherman, architect
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, satire, disaster, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, volleyball, parkour, golf
