 3. the fisherman is the person eating avocado##1
 4. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 7. the architect is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 8. the pilot is the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person eating grapes is between the person who's sport is golf and the person watching musical movies##2
10. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | avocado         | grapes         | kale     | pumpkin      |
| Job           | fisherman | architect | dancer    | pilot     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical      | disaster       | action    | satire       |
| Sport         | handball     | parkour       | golf | volleyball |

