 5. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 7. the pakistani is the person driving the trike##1
 8. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
10. the spanish is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
