3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the train and the person watching comedy movies##2
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
8. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | mirinda   | 7up    | cola  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | family   | comedy | adventure |
