.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, peach, pear, kiwi
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, firefighter, coach, mechanic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, country, dubstep, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, soccer, basketball, climbing
 1. the person eating peach is the coach##1
 2. the person eating kiwi is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the coach is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 4. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the fan of disco is the person eating garlic##1
 6. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
 7. the firefighter is on the left of the coach##1
 8. the fan of country is on the far right##1
 9. the bartender is between the mechanic and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
10. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
