.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, tea, 7up, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, cauliflower, spinach, carrot
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, board-games, sudoku, reading
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, hedgehog, ferret
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating spinach##2
 9. the person eating carrot is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating spinach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up    | iced-tea      | water |
| Food       | pineapple        | carrot       | spinach       | cauliflower     |
| Hobby      | sudoku | traveling | reading | board-games        |
| Pet        | fish       | ferret     | hedgehog         | bird           |

