 4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the mouse##2
 6. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating blueberry##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the ship##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
