4. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the ship##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person driving the motorbike and the owner of the chinchilla##2
6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person eating lettuce is the owner of the goldfish##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating lettuce##1
9. the person drinking milk is the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
